        <alert>Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy Header Missing or Invalid</alert>
        <desc>&lt;p&gt;Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy header is a response header that prevents a document from loading any cross-origin resources that don't explicitly grant the document permission (using CORP or CORS).&lt;/p&gt;</desc>
